Vendor Certification Program — Metrodigi












































































Vendor Certification Program








We take pride in our long-term relationships with our vendors. The Metrodigi Vendor Certification program helps establish and grow our vendor capabilities and expertise so that we can offer gold standard services along with our world-class authoring application. Metrodigi Preferred Vendors complete a three-phase program certifying them for the competencies required to work on a range of Metrodigi digital production projects.This opportunity will be presented to vendors interested in working with Metrodigi. Upon completion of the certification requirements, vendors will be certified as “Metrodigi Preferred Vendors.”























Benefits to VendorsEligibility to accept a wide range of Metrodigi digital production projectsTechnical support, guidance, and full access to Chaucer, MDePubTools and other software solutions related to Metrodigi digital production projectsMetrodigi Preferred Vendor logo for display on all marketing materialsInclusion on Metrodigi’s website and marketing materials, and in presentations to customers as a “Metrodigi Preferred Vendor.” Interested in becoming a Metrodigi Preferred Vendor? Need more information?

