Company Overview of Metrodigi, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Metrodigi, Inc. develops cloud-based content creation software solutions. The company offers Chaucer, a cloud-based content creation and publishing platform that enables publishers to create, manage, and publish interactive digital content. Its Chaucer platform includes tools, such as Visual Content Editor that allows users to author, refine, and collaborate; Chaucer Widget Portal to enhance content with engaging interactivity; Notes to communicate and move work forward; and Track Changes to vet others' edits, maintaining control and consistency in the collaborative process. The company serves customers in higher education, K-12 publishing, sales and marketing, and healthcare markets, as wel...
Metrodigi, Inc. develops cloud-based content creation software solutions. The company offers Chaucer, a cloud-based content creation and publishing platform that enables publishers to create, manage, and publish interactive digital content. Its Chaucer platform includes tools, such as Visual Content Editor that allows users to author, refine, and collaborate; Chaucer Widget Portal to enhance content with engaging interactivity; Notes to communicate and move work forward; and Track Changes to vet others' edits, maintaining control and consistency in the collaborative process. The company serves customers in higher education, K-12 publishing, sales and marketing, and healthcare markets, as well as publishers of comics and graphic novels, cookbooks, art and music books, and children’s books globally. Metrodigi, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Larkspur, California with additional offices in Boston, India, and Ecuador.
